    <p class="hero-eyebrow">// Builder · Automator · Worldbuilder</p>
    <h1 class="hero-name">
      <span class="glitch-wrap" data-text="Ivaylo">Ivaylo</span><br />
      <span class="glitch-wrap" data-text="Kolev">Kolev</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-alias">aka I2KGhost</p>
    <p class="hero-desc">
      I build things at the intersection of <strong>AI automation</strong>, <strong>security research</strong>, and <strong>creative worldbuilding</strong>. Based in London. Always learning, always shipping.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-cta">
      <a href="#projects" class="btn btn-primary">View Projects</a>
      <a href="/about" class="btn btn-ghost">About Me</a>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-tags">
      <span class="tag">Python</span>
      <span class="tag">AI / ML</span>
      <span class="tag">Automation</span>
      <span class="tag">AI Security</span>
      <span class="tag">AWS</span>
      <span class="tag">n8n</span>
      <span class="tag">Astro</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <!-- PROJECTS -->
  <section id="projects">
    <div class="section-geo">
      <div>
        <div class="reveal">
          <p class="section-label">// What I'm building</p>
          <h2 class="section-title">Projects</h2>
          <p class="section-sub">Active work, experiments, and things cooking in the background.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="projects-grid">

          <a href="https://croftguide.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="project-card reveal" style="--card-accent:#3ecfbe;">
            <div class="card-top"><span class="card-tag">Civic Tech · Web</span><span class="card-status status-active">Active</span></div>
            <span class="card-icon">🌱</span>
            <h3 class="card-title">Croft Guide</h3>
            <p class="card-desc">A free tool helping small UK farmers (under 50 acres) understand which government grants and subsidies they qualify for — and how to apply. Built for the SFI 2026 rollout.</p>
          </a>

          <a href="https://tryhackme.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="project-card reveal d1" style="--card-accent:#8b6fff;">
            <div class="card-top"><span class="card-tag">Security · Learning</span><span class="card-status status-learning">In Progress</span></div>
            <span class="card-icon">🔐</span>
            <h3 class="card-title">AI Security Learning Path</h3>
            <p class="card-desc">Working through TryHackMe's AI Security path — threat modelling, prompt injection defence, LLM vulnerabilities, and responsible AI deployment.</p>
          </a>

          <a href="https://aws.amazon.com/training/learn-about/machine-learning/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="project-card reveal d2" style="--card-accent:#c9923a;">
            <div class="card-top"><span class="card-tag">AI / ML · Scholarship</span><span class="card-status status-learning">In Progress</span></div>
            <span class="card-icon">☁️</span>
            <h3 class="card-title">AWS AI & ML Scholars</h3>
            <p class="card-desc">AWS + Udacity global program for 100,000 learners. Hands-on with Amazon Bedrock and PartyRock. Top 4,500 receive a fully funded Nanodegree. Deadline: June 24, 2026.</p>
          </a>

          <a href="https://www.instagram.com/i2kghost" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="project-card reveal" style="--card-accent:#e8b46a;">
            <div class="card-top"><span class="card-tag">Content · Social</span><span class="card-status status-active">Active</span></div>
            <span class="card-icon">📡</span>
            <h3 class="card-title">AI & Robotics — Instagram</h3>
            <p class="card-desc">Building out @i2kghost as a destination for AI tools, robotics, and automation content. Sharing what I learn as I learn it.</p>
          </a>

          <a href="#" class="project-card reveal d1" style="--card-accent:#8b6fff;">
            <div class="card-top"><span class="card-tag">Creative Universe</span><span class="card-status status-paused">On Pause</span></div>
            <span class="card-icon">🐉</span>
            <h3 class="card-title">Drekoria</h3>
            <p class="card-desc">A nature-inspired fantasy universe with its own lore, history, and characters. Past episodes of the Chronicles of Drekoria podcast are still on Spotify.</p>
          </a>

          <a href="#" class="project-card reveal d2" style="--card-accent:#55557a;">
            <div class="card-top"><span class="card-tag">Privacy · Infrastructure</span><span class="card-status status-wip">Ongoing</span></div>
            <span class="card-icon">🛡️</span>
            <h3 class="card-title">Privacy-First Stack</h3>
            <p class="card-desc">De-Googled digital ecosystem: ProtonMail, ProtonDrive, Brave, DuckDuckGo. Documenting the setup, trade-offs, and tools along the way.</p>
          </a>

        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="section-geo-visual" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg width="180" height="500" viewBox="0 0 180 500" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <rect x="20" y="20" width="60" height="60" stroke="#c9923a" stroke-width="1"/><rect x="100" y="20" width="60" height="60" stroke="#c9923a" stroke-width="1"/>
          <rect x="20" y="100" width="60" height="60" stroke="#c9923a" stroke-width="1"/><rect x="100" y="100" width="60" height="60" stroke="#c9923a" stroke-width="1"/>
          <rect x="20" y="180" width="60" height="60" stroke="#3ecfbe" stroke-width="0.7"/><rect x="100" y="180" width="60" height="60" stroke="#3ecfbe" stroke-width="0.7"/>
          <rect x="20" y="260" width="60" height="60" stroke="#3ecfbe" stroke-width="0.5"/><rect x="100" y="260" width="60" height="60" stroke="#3ecfbe" stroke-width="0.5"/>
